    <entry>
      <title>Hexo Quick Start Guide</title>
      <link href="/2019/03/09/hexo-quick-start-guide/"/>
      <url>/2019/03/09/hexo-quick-start-guide/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="Guide"><a href="#Guide" class="headerlink" title="Guide"></a>Guide</h3><h5 id="Install-hexo-globally"><a href="#Install-hexo-globally" class="headerlink" title="Install hexo globally"></a>Install hexo globally</h5><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="Create-your-site"><a href="#Create-your-site" class="headerlink" title="Create your site"></a>Create your site</h5><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="Configurations-see-Configuration"><a href="#Configurations-see-Configuration" class="headerlink" title="Configurations see Configuration"></a>Configurations see <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/configuration" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Configuration</a></h5><h5 id="Deploy-the-site-to-github"><a href="#Deploy-the-site-to-github" class="headerlink" title="Deploy the site to github"></a>Deploy the site to github</h5><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo deploy -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="FIX"><a href="#FIX" class="headerlink" title="FIX"></a>FIX</h3><ul><li><h5 id="The-theme-styles-are-changed-but-not-regenerate"><a href="#The-theme-styles-are-changed-but-not-regenerate" class="headerlink" title="The theme styles are changed but not regenerate"></a>The theme styles are changed but not regenerate</h5><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><h5 id="Code-is-not-support-shell-language-you-can-set-it-with-bash-as-well"><a href="#Code-is-not-support-shell-language-you-can-set-it-with-bash-as-well" class="headerlink" title="Code is not support shell language, you can set it with bash as well"></a>Code is not support <code>shell</code> language, you can set it with <code>bash</code> as well</h5></li><li><h5 id="Hexo-only-support-inline-code-with-format-code"><a href="#Hexo-only-support-inline-code-with-format-code" class="headerlink" title="Hexo only support inline code with format ``code``"></a>Hexo only support inline code with format ``code``</h5></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
